Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friendship! Romance! Mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We try our best because we've made those promises!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the bright convenience store we're known to frequent...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something happens in one of its dark corners!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd you go? It's already so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're staying at Professor Agasa's house tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:02:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing that I caused Haibara's cold to worsen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to stay over and help nurse her until she's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about a change of clothes, and your school things?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brought everything with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that we'll be on winter break soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mind, Ran-neechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ran-neechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to stay here as well, Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it just caring for Ai-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just seems that, as of late...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There have been more and more suspicious people around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a premonition that has me thinking something's going to happen here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:51.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,THE CONVENIENCE STORE TRAP\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can imagine the headache you're getting from these naughty Japanese kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't fret over it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone is a good student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think I have to say "goodbye" to them so soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cannot help but feel very, very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie-sensei is resigning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:04:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to some extenuating family problems back home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She will be officially leaving for America at the end of this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those family problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it has only been for a short while...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be able to learn together with all of you, it made me very, very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while I'm sure there will be some difficulties in your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am confident that you all will be able to overcome them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jodie-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can tell us now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell you about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason that you're resigning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly what are these "family problems"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have looked all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a very, very important treasure map.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I finally found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or so I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A treasure map?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surely, she doesn't mean her first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if that were the case, she wouldn't say it was a map - she'd just say she found the treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't get it with just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no - secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A secret makes a woman, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's a real pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted him to take Sensei's classes as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Shin-ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The type of guy that buries himself in solving cases while leaving his wife alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would never be able to appreciate the merits of Jodie-sensei's lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And exactly how long is he planning to take solving this one case?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should just give up and come back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's just impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:06:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not the type to give up half-way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants to look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I really, really, really like about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I said was that he's a stubborn person who likes to look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if he doesn't come back, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of not coming back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Cool Kid back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The little one with the glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As of late, he's there no matter when I call Doctor Agasa's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? He ran away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know what's good for him - next time I see that little...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like that. He's nursing Ai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that, since it was his fault her cold worsened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He won't be back until she recovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even took a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that little brat has good points, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we have a party at Sensei's apartment right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Party?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be a farewell party for Jodie-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get some snacks and juice from the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go to the convenience store in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one where Aya-chan is working part-time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there such a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was our middle school classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a really cheerful girl - you'll definitely like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a girl by the name of Nanakawa Aya working here, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She s back there with the store manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you so that you'll understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have enough manpower for peak hours as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have any choice but to hire someone new to replace you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened, Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened, Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who are you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fri-en-ds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am a high school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that the money in the register and the stock in the inventory aren't lining up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it only happens to be a problem on Aya-kun's shift when she closes the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you accuse Aya of being at fault based solely on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could just be one of the customers shoplifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, Aya's told us that there are usually a lot of customers in the morning and at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why, when I refurbished the store...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I installed four separate security cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, despite never taking my eyes off them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No such customer ever showed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it has to be a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought of that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I parked my car in front of the store last night and kept watch the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the only one who came out was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aya-kun, when she closed the shutter after cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:18.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From that moment until it was time to open the store, no one came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, after I opened the store and checked the inventory, I found it was off once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only possibility is that Aya-kun is taking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't take them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What types of merchandise were taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:33.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Game software, DVDs, CDs...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bento boxes, onigiri, mineral water, Oolong tea, cola...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as a lot of chocolate, sweets, and snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's easy to picture a group of young people together...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Playing games while listening to music or watching DVDs, and enjoying themselves to their hearts' content.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, supposing the culprit really is Aya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't she be captured on the security cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The security cameras automatically stop recording after closing hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The electricity bill isn't a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the reason the light here is unlit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's to save electricity and make up for losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only ones who come back here to borrow this bathroom are our regulars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's all right if it's a little dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice any suspicious customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say they're "suspicious," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some of the customers did catch my attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there any clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What sort of people are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of them come to borrow the bathroom often.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, give us the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of them looks like a university student.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He comes by occasionally to read the game magazines until closing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A game maniac, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that person has never bought a game at our store before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All he buys are cup noodles and instant food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:11:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's also a really selfish person, always cutting to the front of the checkout line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second one looks like a salaryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's rather timid and especially polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially polite?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His head is always bowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the aforementioned university student cuts in line...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just lets him pay first, without getting angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even when going to the bathroom, he will say, "I'm not in a hurry, you can go first."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The things he buys are toothbrush sets, dry batteries, shavers, and towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are all things you would take on a trip, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The third person is a stubborn and thrifty old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I know that old lady too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She always bargains with me over the bento boxes that have nearly expired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's always insisting that we should learn from the other stores' prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that old lady's not a bad person...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see her switching off lights that aren't in use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:12:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She even mentioned that adjusting the store to a certain temperature would save on the electricity bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, usually, after talking with me for a while, she'll end up leaving without buying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means all three are suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That game maniac student may want to buy the games he's reading strategies for, but can't afford them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The salaryman may like to travel and prefer to take snacks along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old lady may not have bothered to buy anything, but surely there's some bento she wants to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of them are possible culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's best to suspect Aya-kun before moving on to our customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aya is not the kind of person who would do something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, explain it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why it is that, right after I scolded Aya-kun in this very spot just last month, the inventory stopped disappearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing appeared to have been missing this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I actually intended to end surveillance after closing the store last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just as I thought Aya-kun had reflected on her misdeeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I came to the store this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite a bit of the merchandise was missing yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems her urge to steal could not be suppressed any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and apologize, and I'll forgive you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This situation doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we discuss it with Shinichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's him, he'll be able to solve this mystery in no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know Shinichi's phone number...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number doesn't show whenever he calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any brainwaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be saying this if I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how about we try Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that kid often notice interesting things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though, it's a bit embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To resort to asking that bespectacled brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, Conan-kun's at the professor's house, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Relying on someone else without exerting any effort of your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are only a few of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's think of something to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I honestly didn't take anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you still saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the one you rely on most can disappear, at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, hurry up and confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are the culprit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a misunderstanding, Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really didn't take any merchandise from the store!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Conan-kun were here, he'd definitely notice something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we really not make the call, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cool Kid is busy caring for Ai-chan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We mustn't disturb him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if this goes on, Aya will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't need to ask for that brat's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow the Deduction Queen, Sonoko-sama, to solve it for you in the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's begin with an overview of the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:24.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is it the money in the register and the inventory of the store don't match up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, in the end, for some unknown reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:31.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The amount is always short whenever Aya is in charge of cleaning and closing the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, the manager has suspected Aya of taking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But our middle-school classmate, Aya, is a good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, we're investigating in order to name someone else as the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problems so far, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are three customers that Aya found suspicious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One is a game maniac...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks like he's in university.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another is a rather timid but very polite man that appears to be a salaryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the last one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A stubborn old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the three of them often buy here are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:13.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The game maniac only buys cup noodles and instant food...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The salaryman buys toothbrush sets, dry batteries, shavers, and towels as if he were going on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And for the old lady - nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She only talks with the others in the store, without buying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those three all seem suspicious but also not suspicious at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, could it be a shoplifter or a genuine thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I already say that was impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The manager already installed security cameras, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A thief would have "no chance."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is that, in the past, after the manager suspected and scolded her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inventory stopped disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, one month later - yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was once again her turn to mind the store, and again a lot of the inventory disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Aya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does love snacks and juice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's also quite keen on games...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't we trying to prove that Aya is innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this point, if it was Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clues are what differ from the expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever there's a case, there's always something that differs from the norm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all, you have to find those points through careful observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it may seem like something anyone could manage...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if it's something trivial that occurs routinely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's relevant so long as it's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing is more essential than those small changes in the norm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something that differs from the expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, things only disappear on days when Aya is on closing duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you do anything special on the days you're on closing duty, Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just clean the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manager, did you notice anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing in particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be something trivial - anything will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it's nothing big...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The store is especially clean only on the days Aya-chan is on closing duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She neatly arranges the boxes that arrive before the store closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other store assistants and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always leave the arrangement of the boxes to the one who comes in the next morning, and head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You do the same as well, don't you, Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were planning to atone for your misdeeds, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't be taken in by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same for the bento boxes, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ones that go missing are those near their expiration dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:48.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You thought it wouldn't matter since they would be thrown away soon anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But a thief's a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you say we let the police look into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're getting the police!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the lot of you can find them for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shi-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai-kun is still holed up in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She still hasn't recovered from her cold, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I switched the heater on for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, I think it's better to leave her alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's probably listening to those tapes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiho, what you're doing now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom will approve of whatever you choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be rooting for you, so you have to do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, until next time, on your 19th birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye, bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toilet! Toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toilet! Toilet! Toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The line has grown pretty long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are more and more people coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the bathroom line is crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Aya mentioned it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those three suspicious customers borrowed the bathroom often as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, this can wait until after we've served these customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then, head up the cash register.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're not buying anything, could you get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a hindrance to my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aya will...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What exactly should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.34,0:23:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you have eliminated the impossible, whatever remains, however improbable...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind sharing my deduction, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or if it isn't completely accurate...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.19,0:24:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think your deduction's correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.57,0:24:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.49,0:24:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Try it out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.65,0:24:17.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,THE CONVENIENCE STORE TRAP\N(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:22.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Convenience Store Bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.50,0:24:23.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time is the last Conan episode of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.90,0:24:25.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Following that will be a special!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:27.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to Conan's return on January 5th!
